{"tid":2259983,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"涉去年10月1日天橋上向警員掟磚 19歲青年被控非法集結 罪名不成立","createTime":"2020-10-27T08:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T10:56:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ae9aa8b1b7b9e1d487a027ea935ea30a07068a47","tid":2259983,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:33:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10687\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10687&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=22752f03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10687</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第七庭 <br />\n#劉淑嫻裁判官 <br />\n#裁決 <br />\n#1001荃灣 <br />\n<br />\n趙(19) <br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n非法集結<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n被控於19年10月1日，在荃灣荃新天地外的行人天橋與其他身份不詳人士參與非法集結<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">【快訊】罪名不成立 </span></strong>"},{"pid":"7f70987829d4d71a909946e77481f74c62ff398c","tid":2259983,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be35430fa0b0a12ab917c0e388a68ef405cf151","tid":2259983,"uid":19196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:35:43.000Z","msg":"大奇蹟日"},{"pid":"259ebfabddf05d88bc3a6c29ef39b6df866e81b3","tid":2259983,"uid":8014,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:35:59.000Z","msg":"DOJoke 唔上訴我切柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0169c46499ae88d64a1afcca8f2d6897b599af33","tid":2259983,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:36:42.000Z","msg":"上月審訊摘要:<br />\n<br />\n案件9月30日於西九龍裁判法院開審。警署警長供稱，當時在天橋下看見身穿白色上衣的人掟磚；辯方質疑，現場新聞片段拍攝不到有人掟磚，當時很多人身穿白色上衣，質疑警長認錯人。<br />\n<br />\n時任新界南衝鋒隊的警署警長劉世明供稱，當日有情報指荃灣市中心一帶有人堵路及向警察投擲雜物，他遂帶領防暴警員到案發地點執勤。案發時，劉稱看見行人天橋上有3名男子向警方掟磚 ，其中1名身穿白色上衣、戴鴨嘴帽及防毒面罩，其餘兩人則穿黑色上衣。<br />\n<br />\n劉供稱當時有警員以大聲公作出警告，並登上天橋作出調查，有3人走向在場10多名黑衣人後方。劉指被告看見到場的警員，突然轉身跑向荃新天地，並在商場門前脫下防毒面罩、護目鏡、帽子及手套扔到地上，警方上前截停並拘捕他。<br />\n<br />\n辯方在庭上播放1段在網上找到的新聞片段，並向劉指出，該片段拍攝不到有人掟磚，更沒有拍到白衣人掟磚，劉表示認同。辯方又指出，片段顯示除被告外，商場門前還有很多身穿白色上衣的人，劉亦同意。"},{"pid":"3d5e57175f4314ed9ab516ab292b43a1d15b1948","tid":2259983,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f70987829d4d71a909946e77481f74c62ff398c","tid":2259983,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a986a1f49156d47af9735987f5a44b1428773e18","tid":2259983,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8be35430fa0b0a12ab917c0e388a68ef405cf151","tid":2259983,"uid":19196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:35:43.000Z","msg":"大奇蹟日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99030276026a0d305470cc8e068da013a37c3d27","tid":2259983,"u